Package: emglasso
Title: EM-Based Gaussian Mixture Models with Sparse Covariance via Graphical LASSO
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Harrison", "Watts", email = "hrwatts@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Implements a two-stage algorithm for model-based clustering in high-dimensional data
    with sparse covariance structure estimation. The method combines the EM algorithm 
    for Gaussian mixture models with graphical LASSO regularization to estimate sparse 
    precision (inverse covariance) matrices for each mixture component. This approach 
    enables simultaneous clustering and discovery of conditional independence structures
    within each cluster.
